'''''Cape Town Affair''' ni''  filime y'ubutasi yakozwe na 20 Century Fox kuri Studiyo ya Killarney muri Afrika yepfo iyoborwa na Robert D. Webb muri 1967<ref>https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b6a716447</ref>. Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Claire Trevor, James Brolin, na Jacqueline Bisset<ref>https://www.senscritique.com/film/The_cape_town_affair/460067</ref>. Nibisubirwamo by'amafoto 1953 ''[[:en:Pickup_on_South_Street|Pickup on South Street]]''.<ref>https://www.ejumpcut.org/archive/jc47.2005/capetown/2.html</ref>Nibwo bwa mbere Brolin yakinnye We na Bisset bombi bagiranye amasezerano na Fox<ref>https://www.senscritique.com/film/The_Cape_Town_Affair/460067/details</ref><ref>https://www.loot.co.za/product/james-brolin-the-cape-town-affair/mjfg-1619-g390</ref>. Nyuma yaje kuvuga ati "Sinigeze nkunda cyane ariko twe [we na Bisset] ntabwo twari babi.<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film922453.html</ref>" 

